  "detailed_description": "In this small and dark match 3 game you will put at least three of the same items in a row. At each level you will have a limited amount of movement. Collect the minimum number of points to complete the level and proceed to the next.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dark atmosphere of excavations, artifacts and relics.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoyable music enhances the immersion.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Random generation of levels of varying degrees of difficulty.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A unique playing field for each level.</li></ul>",
